OL,3,CBurnham to meet Swinney for first time
OL,4,Cas Prime Minister during Scotland visit
OL,6,FAndy Burnham will meet with First
OL,7,FMinister John Swinney during his visit
OL,8,Fto Scotland for the Commonwealth Games.
OL,10,FIt's the first in-person meeting
OL,11,Fbetween the Scottish and UK leaders
OL,12,Fsince Mr Burnham became Prime Minister
OL,13,Fon Monday.
OL,15,FThe Labour leader signalled he did not
OL,16,Fwant to discuss the prospect of
OL,17,Fanother independence referendum with
OL,18,Fthe SNP leader.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
