OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784767668
OL,3,CBurnham to meet Swinney for first time
OL,4,Cas Prime Minister during Scotland visit
OL,6,FMr Burnham will arrive in Glasgow on
OL,7,FThursday to watch the opening ceremony
OL,8,Ffor the 2026 Commonwealth Games, where
OL,9,Fhe will be joined by the King and
OL,10,FQueen.
OL,12,FHe will also meet the First Minister
OL,13,Fof Wales, Rhun ap Iorwerth.
OL,15,FThe UK Government has said Mr Burnham
OL,16,Fwould set out how he plans to work
OL,17,F"collaboratively" with devolved
OL,18,Fgovernments "based on a genuine
OL,19,Fpartnership".
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@QO]zD@MOU{D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784767668
OL,3,CBurnham to meet Swinney for first time
OL,4,Cas Prime Minister during Scotland visit
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister said: "When I say
OL,7,Fwe need good growth in every postcode,
OL,8,FI mean every postcode across the whole
OL,9,Fof the UK. Every place and every
OL,10,Fperson matters.
OL,12,F"I'm not focused on point scoring or
OL,13,Fdiscussing constitutional changes like
OL,14,Freferendums, I want practical measures
OL,15,Fto help people live well and bring
OL,16,Fback hope.
OL,26,@nD@ZOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784767668
OL,3,CBurnham to meet Swinney for first time
OL,4,Cas Prime Minister during Scotland visit
OL,6,F"That's why I'm giving families more
OL,7,Fbreathing space with help on the cost
OL,8,Fof living, which I have started this
OL,9,Fweek by taking VAT off electricity
OL,10,Fbills, saving money for millions of
OL,11,Fhouseholds."
OL,13,FThe PM is expected to meet with the
OL,14,FFirst Minister and Deputy First
OL,15,FMinister of Northern Ireland on his
OL,16,Ftour of the UK in August, where he
OL,17,Fwill visit areas across Scotland,
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland, Wales and England.
OL,20,FThursday will mark Mr Burnham's second
OL,21,Fconversation with Mr Swinney.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784767668
OL,3,CBurnham to meet Swinney for first time
OL,4,Cas Prime Minister during Scotland visit
OL,6,FDuring a phone call with the Scottish
OL,7,Fleader on Tuesday morning, Mr Burnham
OL,8,Fis said to have shut down the prospect
OL,9,Fof a second independence referendum,
OL,10,Fwith a UK Government source saying the
OL,11,FPM told the First Minister they will
OL,12,Fhave to "agree to disagree".
OL,14,FIt's understood Mr Burnham, who has
OL,15,Fsaid he wants to devolve more powers
OL,16,Fthroughout the UK, pledged to work
OL,17,Fwith the Scottish Government to
OL,18,Fdeliver a "new kind of politics".
OL,26,@tD@IOUtD@[O]zD@KOUzD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
