SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784767668
OL,3,CBurnham to meet Swinney for first time
OL,4,Cas Prime Minister during Scotland visit
OL,6,FHowever, Swinney has signalled he does
OL,7,Fnot want to work with Douglas
OL,8,FAlexander, the Scottish Secretary,
OL,9,Fafter Mr Burnham decided to keep him
OL,10,Fin the post.
OL,12,FThe First Minister told the Press
OL,13,FAssociation he would rather deal with
OL,14,Fthe Prime Minister one-on-one, having
OL,15,Faccused Mr Alexander of souring
OL,16,Frelations between the UK and Scottish
OL,17,Fgovernments.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
