PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784767668
OL,3,CBurnham to meet Swinney for first time
OL,4,Cas Prime Minister during Scotland visit
OL,6,FMr Burnham's visit to Scotland marks a
OL,7,Fchange from his successor, with Sir
OL,8,FKeir Starmer choosing not to campaign
OL,9,Fin Scotland for the Holyrood election.
OL,11,FScottish Labour figures have pointed
OL,12,Fto Sir Keir as the reason for the
OL,13,Fparty's Holyrood election results in
OL,14,FMay ` its worst in the history of
OL,15,Fdevolution.
OL,17,FMr Burnham is poised to make Scottish
OL,18,FLabour leader Anas Sarwar a minister,
OL,19,Fa move that will see him leave the
OL,20,FScottish Parliament and head to the
OL,21,FHouse of Lords.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784767668
OL,3,CBurnham to meet Swinney for first time
OL,4,Cas Prime Minister during Scotland visit
OL,6,FThe First Minister of Wales said: "I
OL,7,Flook forward to meeting the Prime
OL,8,FMinister in Glasgow today.
OL,10,F"It is fitting that we meet in
OL,11,FScotland, as it underlines Wales' case
OL,12,Ffor parity of powers and a fairer
OL,13,Ffunding model that reflects our needs.
OL,26,@nD@cOUrD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784767668
OL,3,CBurnham to meet Swinney for first time
OL,4,Cas Prime Minister during Scotland visit
OL,6,F"'Number 10 North' must not become
OL,7,Fjust Whitehall with a different
OL,8,Fpostcode. I agree wholeheartedly on
OL,9,Fempowering communities ` it's at the
OL,10,Fheart of my politics ` but decisions
OL,11,Faffecting Wales should be made in
OL,12,FWales, and it is for the Welsh
OL,13,FGovernment and our Senedd to work with
OL,14,Fthe people of Wales on how power is
OL,15,Fexercised and shared within our nation.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784767668
OL,3,CBurnham to meet Swinney for first time
OL,4,Cas Prime Minister during Scotland visit
OL,6,F"At a time when families are still
OL,7,Ffeeling the pressure of the cost of
OL,8,Fliving, I am also keen to discuss how
OL,9,Four governments can work together as
OL,10,Fequal partners to deliver improvements
OL,11,Fto the lives of people in Wales."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
